{"tid":520304,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"而家D升學中心真係相當唔專業 垃圾！！","createTime":"2018-01-05T09:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T09:56:57.000Z","uid":164491,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c0742f26f52d1dceba4b0bdc30848ec6efa4f566","tid":520304,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:29:45.000Z","msg":"我係香港讀完DEGREE 唸住過澳洲讀書<br />\n自己睇左好多資料 知道可以讀2年就完<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知打左3間比較大型既升學中心<br />\n一口氣就話最少要讀3年<br />\n我心唸無理由 我明明係個網到睇到2年<br />\n又無ADDITIONAL REQUIREMENT<br />\n<br />\n仲要有一間係專做澳洲升學<br />\n係澳洲都有OFFICE 既  第一句就話做左咁耐無做過2年既CASE<br />\n<br />\n如果我唔係自己做好RESEARCH <br />\n就咁信你地講野<br />\n我分分鍾己經唔會唸留學呢條路<br />\n<br />\n建議大家唔好懶<br />\n唔好靠佢地<br />\n就算唔識都好 問多幾間 <br />\n特登開POST 係感受到事件既嚴重性<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a492b04fb3491acca14de9feeb41d29198b3c8f","tid":520304,"uid":127177,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:48:59.000Z","msg":"讀3年啊傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe8ad43a8e76b088e1ecd8e5a2cf8d230110ca6","tid":520304,"uid":117009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:50:53.000Z","msg":"你讀咩先？有無學校官網 link?"},{"pid":"3857b2e3725fbb2856f7313a33ebd3b1278adc2f","tid":520304,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T12:33:28.000Z","msg":"咁你讀完未"},{"pid":"d4d8909e613cd5b46e75d01658091eb6c402cc26","tid":520304,"uid":142707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"